# Frontend Architecture

## Stack

Framework:
Next.js 15 App Router

Language:
TypeScript Strict Mode

Styling:
Tailwind CSS

Motion:
Framer Motion

Scroll:
Lenis

Components:
Shadcn UI (heavily customized)

## Principles

- Server Components first
- Client Components only when needed
- Strict typing everywhere
- Reusable architecture
- Semantic HTML

Always use:

<main>
<nav>
<section>
<article>
<footer>

Avoid div soup.
